195WebProcessPool::WebProcessPool(API::ProcessPoolConfiguration& configuration)
196 : m_configuration(configuration.copy())
197 , m_defaultPageGroup(WebPageGroup::create())
198 , m_injectedBundleClient(makeUnique<API::InjectedBundleClient>())
199 , m_automationClient(makeUnique<API::AutomationClient>())
200 , m_historyClient(makeUnique<API::LegacyContextHistoryClient>())
201 , m_visitedLinkStore(VisitedLinkStore::create())
202#if PLATFORM(MAC)
203 , m_highPerformanceGraphicsUsageSampler(makeUnique<HighPerformanceGraphicsUsageSampler>(*this))
204 , m_perActivityStateCPUUsageSampler(makeUnique<PerActivityStateCPUUsageSampler>(*this))
205#endif
206 , m_alwaysRunsAtBackgroundPriority(m_configuration->alwaysRunsAtBackgroundPriority())
207 , m_shouldTakeUIBackgroundAssertion(m_configuration->shouldTakeUIBackgroundAssertion())
208 , m_userObservablePageCounter([this](RefCounterEvent) { updateProcessSuppressionState(); })
209 , m_processSuppressionDisabledForPageCounter([this](RefCounterEvent) { updateProcessSuppressionState(); })
210 , m_hiddenPageThrottlingAutoIncreasesCounter([this](RefCounterEvent) { m_hiddenPageThrottlingTimer.startOneShot(0_s); })
211 , m_hiddenPageThrottlingTimer(RunLoop::main(), this, &WebProcessPool::updateHiddenPageThrottlingAutoIncreaseLimit)
212#if ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
213 , m_resetGPUProcessCrashCountTimer(RunLoop::main(), [this] { m_recentGPUProcessCrashCount = 0; })
214#endif
215 , m_foregroundWebProcessCounter([this](RefCounterEvent) { updateProcessAssertions(); })
216 , m_backgroundWebProcessCounter([this](RefCounterEvent) { updateProcessAssertions(); })
217 , m_backForwardCache(makeUniqueRef<WebBackForwardCache>(*this))
218 , m_webProcessCache(makeUniqueRef<WebProcessCache>(*this))
219 , m_webProcessWithAudibleMediaCounter([this](RefCounterEvent) { updateAudibleMediaAssertions(); })
220{
221 static std::once_flag onceFlag;
222 std::call_once(onceFlag, [] {
223 WTF::setProcessPrivileges(allPrivileges());
224 WebCore::NetworkStorageSession::permitProcessToUseCookieAPI(true);
225 Process::setIdentifier(WebCore::ProcessIdentifier::generate());
226#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
227 determineITPState();
228#endif
229 });
230
231 for (auto& scheme : m_configuration->alwaysRevalidatedURLSchemes())
232 m_schemesToRegisterAsAlwaysRevalidated.add(scheme);
233
234 for (const auto& urlScheme : m_configuration->cachePartitionedURLSchemes())
235 m_schemesToRegisterAsCachePartitioned.add(urlScheme);
236
237 platformInitialize();
238
239#if OS(LINUX)
240 MemoryPressureMonitor::singleton().start();
241#endif
242
243 addMessageReceiver(Messages::WebProcessPool::messageReceiverName(), *this);
244
245 // NOTE: These sub-objects must be initialized after m_messageReceiverMap..
246 addSupplement<WebGeolocationManagerProxy>();
247 addSupplement<WebNotificationManagerProxy>();
248
249 processPools().append(this);
250
251 resolvePathsForSandboxExtensions();
252
253#if !LOG_DISABLED || !RELEASE_LOG_DISABLED
254 WebCore::initializeLogChannelsIfNecessary();
255 WebKit::initializeLogChannelsIfNecessary();
256#endif // !LOG_DISABLED || !RELEASE_LOG_DISABLED
257
258#ifndef NDEBUG
259 processPoolCounter.increment();
260#endif
261
262 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
263
264 updateBackForwardCacheCapacity();
265
266#if PLATFORM(IOS)
267 if (WebCore::IOSApplication::isLutron() && !WebCore::linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstWithSharedNetworkProcess)) {
268 callOnMainRunLoop([] {
269 if (WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStoreExists())
270 WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStore()->terminateNetworkProcess();
271 });
272 }
273#endif
274}
275
276WebProcessPool::~WebProcessPool()
277{
278 m_webProcessCache->clear();
279
280 bool removed = processPools().removeFirst(this);
281 ASSERT_UNUSED(removed, removed);
282
283 m_messageReceiverMap.invalidate();
284
285 for (auto& supplement : m_supplements.values()) {
286 supplement->processPoolDestroyed();
287 supplement->clearProcessPool();
288 }
289
290 platformInvalidateContext();
291
292#ifndef NDEBUG
293 processPoolCounter.decrement();
294#endif
295
296#if ENABLE(GAMEPAD)
297 if (!m_processesUsingGamepads.computesEmpty())
298 UIGamepadProvider::singleton().processPoolStoppedUsingGamepads(*this);
299#endif
300
301 // Only remaining processes should be pre-warmed ones as other keep the process pool alive.
302 while (!m_processes.isEmpty()) {
303 auto& process = m_processes.first();
304
305 ASSERT(process->isPrewarmed());
306 // We need to be the only one holding a reference to the pre-warmed process so that it gets destroyed.
307 // WebProcessProxies currently always expect to have a WebProcessPool.
308 ASSERT(process->hasOneRef());
309
310 process->shutDown();
311 }
312
313 if (processPools().isEmpty() && !!NetworkProcessProxy::defaultNetworkProcess())
314 NetworkProcessProxy::defaultNetworkProcess() = nullptr;
315}

411void WebProcessPool::networkProcessDidTerminate(NetworkProcessProxy& networkProcessProxy, NetworkProcessProxy::TerminationReason reason)
412{
413 for (auto& supplement : m_supplements.values())
414 supplement->processDidClose(&networkProcessProxy);
415
416 if (reason == NetworkProcessProxy::TerminationReason::Crash)
417 m_client.networkProcessDidCrash(this);
418
419 if (m_automationSession)
420 m_automationSession->terminate();
421
422 terminateServiceWorkers();
423}

440void WebProcessPool::gpuProcessExited(ProcessID identifier, GPUProcessTerminationReason reason)
441{
442 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(Process, "gpuProcessDidExit: PID=%d, reason=%u", identifier, static_cast<unsigned>(reason));
443 m_gpuProcess = nullptr;
444
445 if (reason == GPUProcessTerminationReason::Crash || reason == GPUProcessTerminationReason::Unresponsive)
446 m_client.gpuProcessDidCrash(this, identifier);
447
448 Vector<Ref<WebProcessProxy>> processes = m_processes;
449 for (auto& process : processes)
450 process->gpuProcessExited(reason);
451
452 if (reason == GPUProcessTerminationReason::Crash || reason == GPUProcessTerminationReason::Unresponsive) {
453 if (++m_recentGPUProcessCrashCount > maximumGPUProcessRelaunchAttemptsBeforeKillingWebProcesses) {
454 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Process, "gpuProcessDidExit: GPU Process has crashed more than %u times in the last %g seconds, terminating all WebProcesses", maximumGPUProcessRelaunchAttemptsBeforeKillingWebProcesses, resetGPUProcessCrashCountDelay.seconds());
455 m_resetGPUProcessCrashCountTimer.stop();
456 m_recentGPUProcessCrashCount = 0;
457 terminateAllWebContentProcesses();
458 } else if (!m_resetGPUProcessCrashCountTimer.isActive())
459 m_resetGPUProcessCrashCountTimer.startOneShot(resetGPUProcessCrashCountDelay);
460 }
461}

463void WebProcessPool::getGPUProcessConnection(WebProcessProxy& webProcessProxy, GPUProcessConnectionParameters&& parameters, Messages::WebProcessProxy::GetGPUProcessConnection::DelayedReply&& reply)
464{
465#if ENABLE(IPC_TESTING_API)
466 parameters.ignoreInvalidMessageForTesting = webProcessProxy.ignoreInvalidMessageForTesting();
467#endif
468 ensureGPUProcess().getGPUProcessConnection(webProcessProxy, parameters, [this, weakThis = makeWeakPtr(*this), parameters, webProcessProxy = makeWeakPtr(webProcessProxy), reply = WTFMove(reply)] (auto& connectionInfo) mutable {
469 if (UNLIKELY(!IPC::Connection::identifierIsValid(connectionInfo.identifier()))) {
470 // Retry on the next RunLoop iteration because we may be inside the WebProcessPool destructor.
471 RunLoop::main().dispatch([this, weakThis = WTFMove(weakThis), webProcessProxy = WTFMove(webProcessProxy), parameters = WTFMove(parameters), reply = WTFMove(reply)] () mutable {
472 if (weakThis && webProcessProxy) {
473 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Process, "getGPUProcessConnection: Failed first attempt, retrying");
474 ensureGPUProcess().getGPUProcessConnection(*webProcessProxy, parameters, WTFMove(reply));
475 } else
476 reply({ });
477 });
478 return;
479 }
480 reply(connectionInfo);
481 });
482}
483#endif

499bool WebProcessPool::s_useSeparateServiceWorkerProcess = false;
500
501#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
502void WebProcessPool::establishWorkerContextConnectionToNetworkProcess(NetworkProcessProxy& proxy, RegistrableDomain&& registrableDomain, PAL::SessionID sessionID, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
503{
504 auto* websiteDataStore = WebsiteDataStore::existingDataStoreForSessionID(sessionID);
505 if (!websiteDataStore)
506 websiteDataStore = WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStore().ptr();
507 if (!processPools().size())
508 static NeverDestroyed<Ref<WebProcessPool>> serviceWorkerProcessPool(WebProcessPool::create(API::ProcessPoolConfiguration::create().get()));
509
510 // Arbitrarily choose the first process pool to host the service worker process.
511 auto* processPool = processPools()[0];
512 ASSERT(processPool);
513
514 WebProcessProxy* serviceWorkerProcessProxy { nullptr };
515
516 if (!s_useSeparateServiceWorkerProcess) {
517 for (auto& process : processPool->m_processes) {
518 if (process.ptr() == processPool->m_prewarmedProcess.get() || process->isDummyProcessProxy())
519 continue;
520 if (&process->websiteDataStore() != websiteDataStore)
521 continue;
522 if (!process->isMatchingRegistrableDomain(registrableDomain))
523 continue;
524
525 serviceWorkerProcessProxy = process.ptr();
526 serviceWorkerProcessProxy->enableServiceWorkers(processPool->userContentControllerIdentifierForServiceWorkers());
527
528 if (serviceWorkerProcessProxy->isInProcessCache()) {
529 processPool->webProcessCache().removeProcess(*serviceWorkerProcessProxy, WebProcessCache::ShouldShutDownProcess::No);
530 ASSERT(!serviceWorkerProcessProxy->isInProcessCache());
531 }
532
533 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG_STATIC(ServiceWorker, "establishWorkerContextConnectionToNetworkProcess reusing an existing web process (process=%p, PID=%d)", serviceWorkerProcessProxy, serviceWorkerProcessProxy->processIdentifier());
534 break;
535 }
536 }
537
538 if (!serviceWorkerProcessProxy) {
539 auto newProcessProxy = WebProcessProxy::createForServiceWorkers(*processPool, WTFMove(registrableDomain), *websiteDataStore);
540 serviceWorkerProcessProxy = newProcessProxy.ptr();
541
542 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG_STATIC(ServiceWorker, "establishWorkerContextConnectionToNetworkProcess creating a new service worker process (proces=%p, PID=%d)", serviceWorkerProcessProxy, serviceWorkerProcessProxy->processIdentifier());
543
544 processPool->initializeNewWebProcess(newProcessProxy, websiteDataStore);
545 processPool->m_processes.append(WTFMove(newProcessProxy));
546 }
547
548 ASSERT(!serviceWorkerProcesses().contains(*serviceWorkerProcessProxy));
549 serviceWorkerProcesses().add(*serviceWorkerProcessProxy);
550
551 serviceWorkerProcessProxy->establishServiceWorkerContext(processPool->m_serviceWorkerPreferences ? processPool->m_serviceWorkerPreferences.value() : processPool->m_defaultPageGroup->preferences().store(), WTFMove(completionHandler));
552 if (!processPool->m_serviceWorkerUserAgent.isNull())
553 serviceWorkerProcessProxy->setServiceWorkerUserAgent(processPool->m_serviceWorkerUserAgent);
554}
555
556void WebProcessPool::removeFromServiceWorkerProcesses(WebProcessProxy& process)
557{
558 ASSERT(serviceWorkerProcesses().contains(process));
559 serviceWorkerProcesses().remove(process);
560}
561#endif

585void WebProcessPool::resolvePathsForSandboxExtensions()
586{
587 m_resolvedPaths.injectedBundlePath = resolvePathForSandboxExtension(injectedBundlePath());
588
589 m_resolvedPaths.additionalWebProcessSandboxExtensionPaths.reserveCapacity(m_configuration->additionalReadAccessAllowedPaths().size());

592

594}

596Ref<WebProcessProxy> WebProcessPool::createNewWebProcess(WebsiteDataStore* websiteDataStore, WebProcessProxy::IsPrewarmed isPrewarmed)
597{
598#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
599 m_tccPreferenceEnabled = doesAppHaveITPEnabled();
600 if (websiteDataStore && !websiteDataStore->isItpStateExplicitlySet())
601 websiteDataStore->setResourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(m_tccPreferenceEnabled);
602#endif
603
604 auto processProxy = WebProcessProxy::create(*this, websiteDataStore, isPrewarmed);
605 initializeNewWebProcess(processProxy, websiteDataStore, isPrewarmed);
606 m_processes.append(processProxy.copyRef());
607
608 return processProxy;
609}
610
611RefPtr<WebProcessProxy> WebProcessPool::tryTakePrewarmedProcess(WebsiteDataStore& websiteDataStore)
612{
613 if (!m_prewarmedProcess)
614 return nullptr;
615
616 // There is sometimes a delay until we get notified that a prewarmed process has been terminated (e.g. after resuming
617 // from suspension) so make sure the process is still running here before deciding to use it.
618 if (m_prewarmedProcess->wasTerminated()) {
619 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Process, "tryTakePrewarmedProcess: Not using prewarmed process because it has been terminated (process=%p, PID=%d)", m_prewarmedProcess.get(), m_prewarmedProcess->processIdentifier());
620 m_prewarmedProcess = nullptr;
621 return nullptr;
622 }
623
624#if PLATFORM(GTK) || PLATFORM(WPE)
625 // In platforms using Bubblewrap for sandboxing, prewarmed process is launched using the WebProcessPool primary WebsiteDataStore,
626 // so we don't use it in case of using a different WebsiteDataStore.
627 if (m_sandboxEnabled)
628 return nullptr;
629#endif
630
631 ASSERT(m_prewarmedProcess->isPrewarmed());
632 m_prewarmedProcess->setWebsiteDataStore(websiteDataStore);
633 m_prewarmedProcess->markIsNoLongerInPrewarmedPool();
634
635 return std::exchange(m_prewarmedProcess, nullptr).get();
636}

667WebProcessDataStoreParameters WebProcessPool::webProcessDataStoreParameters(WebProcessProxy& process, WebsiteDataStore& websiteDataStore)
668{
669 websiteDataStore.resolveDirectoriesIfNecessary();
670
671 String applicationCacheDirectory = websiteDataStore.resolvedApplicationCacheDirectory();
672 SandboxExtension::Handle applicationCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle;
673 if (!applicationCacheDirectory.isEmpty())
674 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(applicationCacheDirectory, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, applicationCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle);
675
676 String applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName = websiteDataStore.applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName();
677
678 String mediaCacheDirectory = websiteDataStore.resolvedMediaCacheDirectory();
679 SandboxExtension::Handle mediaCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle;
680 if (!mediaCacheDirectory.isEmpty())
681 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(mediaCacheDirectory, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, mediaCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle);
682
683 String mediaKeyStorageDirectory = websiteDataStore.resolvedMediaKeysDirectory();
684 SandboxExtension::Handle mediaKeyStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle;
685 if (!mediaKeyStorageDirectory.isEmpty())
686 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(mediaKeyStorageDirectory, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, mediaKeyStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
687
688 String javaScriptConfigurationDirectory;
689 if (!m_javaScriptConfigurationDirectory.isEmpty())
690 javaScriptConfigurationDirectory = resolvePathForSandboxExtension(m_javaScriptConfigurationDirectory);
691 else if (javaScriptConfigurationFileEnabled())
692 javaScriptConfigurationDirectory = websiteDataStore.resolvedJavaScriptConfigurationDirectory();
693
694 SandboxExtension::Handle javaScriptConfigurationDirectoryExtensionHandle;
695 if (!javaScriptConfigurationDirectory.isEmpty())
696 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(javaScriptConfigurationDirectory, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, javaScriptConfigurationDirectoryExtensionHandle);
697
698#if HAVE(ARKIT_INLINE_PREVIEW)
699 auto modelElementCacheDirectory = websiteDataStore.resolvedModelElementCacheDirectory();
700 SandboxExtension::Handle modelElementCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle;
701 if (!modelElementCacheDirectory.isEmpty())
702 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(modelElementCacheDirectory, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, modelElementCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle);
703#endif
704
705 return WebProcessDataStoreParameters {
706 websiteDataStore.sessionID(),
707 WTFMove(applicationCacheDirectory),
708 WTFMove(applicationCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle),
709 WTFMove(applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName),
710 WTFMove(mediaCacheDirectory),
711 WTFMove(mediaCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle),
712 WTFMove(mediaKeyStorageDirectory),
713 WTFMove(mediaKeyStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle),
714 WTFMove(javaScriptConfigurationDirectory),
715 WTFMove(javaScriptConfigurationDirectoryExtensionHandle),
716#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
717 websiteDataStore.thirdPartyCookieBlockingMode(),
718 m_domainsWithUserInteraction,
719 m_domainsWithCrossPageStorageAccessQuirk,
720#endif
721#if HAVE(ARKIT_INLINE_PREVIEW)
722 WTFMove(modelElementCacheDirectory),
723 WTFMove(modelElementCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle),
724#endif
725 websiteDataStore.resourceLoadStatisticsEnabled()
726 };
727}

729void WebProcessPool::initializeNewWebProcess(WebProcessProxy& process, WebsiteDataStore* websiteDataStore, WebProcessProxy::IsPrewarmed isPrewarmed)
730{
731 auto initializationActivity = process.throttler().backgroundActivity("WebProcess initialization"_s);
732 auto scopeExit = makeScopeExit([&process, initializationActivity = WTFMove(initializationActivity)]() mutable {
733 // Round-trip to the Web Content process before releasing the
734 // initialization activity, so that we're sure that all
735 // messages sent from this function have been handled.
736 process.isResponsive([initializationActivity = WTFMove(initializationActivity)] (bool) { });
737 });
738
739 WebProcessCreationParameters parameters;
740
741 parameters.injectedBundlePath = m_resolvedPaths.injectedBundlePath;
742 if (!parameters.injectedBundlePath.isEmpty())
743 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(parameters.injectedBundlePath, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadOnly, parameters.injectedBundlePathExtensionHandle);
744
745 parameters.additionalSandboxExtensionHandles.allocate(m_resolvedPaths.additionalWebProcessSandboxExtensionPaths.size());
746 for (size_t i = 0, size = m_resolvedPaths.additionalWebProcessSandboxExtensionPaths.size(); i < size; ++i)
747 SandboxExtension::createHandleWithoutResolvingPath(m_resolvedPaths.additionalWebProcessSandboxExtensionPaths[i], SandboxExtension::Type::ReadOnly, parameters.additionalSandboxExtensionHandles[i]);
748
749#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
750 setJavaScriptConfigurationFileEnabledFromDefaults();
751#endif
752
753 parameters.cacheModel = LegacyGlobalSettings::singleton().cacheModel();
754 parameters.overrideLanguages = configuration().overrideLanguages();
755
756 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsEmptyDocument = copyToVector(m_schemesToRegisterAsEmptyDocument);
757 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsSecure = copyToVector(LegacyGlobalSettings::singleton().schemesToRegisterAsSecure());
758 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsBypassingContentSecurityPolicy = copyToVector(LegacyGlobalSettings::singleton().schemesToRegisterAsBypassingContentSecurityPolicy());
759 parameters.urlSchemesForWhichDomainRelaxationIsForbidden = copyToVector(m_schemesToSetDomainRelaxationForbiddenFor);
760 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsLocal = copyToVector(LegacyGlobalSettings::singleton().schemesToRegisterAsLocal());
761 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsNoAccess = copyToVector(LegacyGlobalSettings::singleton().schemesToRegisterAsNoAccess());
762 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsDisplayIsolated = copyToVector(m_schemesToRegisterAsDisplayIsolated);
763 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsCORSEnabled = copyToVector(m_schemesToRegisterAsCORSEnabled);
764 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsAlwaysRevalidated = copyToVector(m_schemesToRegisterAsAlwaysRevalidated);
765 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsCachePartitioned = copyToVector(m_schemesToRegisterAsCachePartitioned);
766 parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsCanDisplayOnlyIfCanRequest = copyToVector(m_schemesToRegisterAsCanDisplayOnlyIfCanRequest);
767
768 parameters.shouldAlwaysUseComplexTextCodePath = m_alwaysUsesComplexTextCodePath;
769 parameters.shouldUseFontSmoothing = m_shouldUseFontSmoothing;
770
771 parameters.terminationTimeout = 0_s;
772
773 parameters.textCheckerState = TextChecker::state();
774
775 parameters.fullKeyboardAccessEnabled = WebProcessProxy::fullKeyboardAccessEnabled();
776
777 parameters.defaultRequestTimeoutInterval = API::URLRequest::defaultTimeoutInterval();
778
779 parameters.backForwardCacheCapacity = backForwardCache().capacity();
780
781#if ENABLE(NOTIFICATIONS)
782 // FIXME: There should be a generic way for supplements to add to the intialization parameters.
783 parameters.notificationPermissions = supplement<WebNotificationManagerProxy>()->notificationPermissions();
784#endif
785
786 parameters.memoryCacheDisabled = m_memoryCacheDisabled;
787 parameters.attrStyleEnabled = m_configuration->attrStyleEnabled();
788 parameters.shouldThrowExceptionForGlobalConstantRedeclaration = m_configuration->shouldThrowExceptionForGlobalConstantRedeclaration();
789
790#if ENABLE(SERVICE_CONTROLS)
791 auto& serviceController = ServicesController::singleton();
792 parameters.hasImageServices = serviceController.hasImageServices();
793 parameters.hasSelectionServices = serviceController.hasSelectionServices();
794 parameters.hasRichContentServices = serviceController.hasRichContentServices();
795 serviceController.refreshExistingServices();
796#endif
797
798#if OS(LINUX)
799 parameters.shouldEnableMemoryPressureReliefLogging = true;
800#endif
801
802 parameters.presentingApplicationPID = m_configuration->presentingApplicationPID();
803
804 // Add any platform specific parameters
805 platformInitializeWebProcess(process, parameters);
806
807 RefPtr<API::Object> injectedBundleInitializationUserData = m_injectedBundleClient->getInjectedBundleInitializationUserData(*this);
808 if (!injectedBundleInitializationUserData)
809 injectedBundleInitializationUserData = m_injectedBundleInitializationUserData;
810 parameters.initializationUserData = UserData(process.transformObjectsToHandles(injectedBundleInitializationUserData.get()));
811
812 if (websiteDataStore)
813 parameters.websiteDataStoreParameters = webProcessDataStoreParameters(process, *websiteDataStore);
814
815 process.send(Messages::WebProcess::InitializeWebProcess(parameters), 0);
816
817 if (m_automationSession)
818 process.send(Messages::WebProcess::EnsureAutomationSessionProxy(m_automationSession->sessionIdentifier()), 0);
819
820 ASSERT(m_messagesToInjectedBundlePostedToEmptyContext.isEmpty());
821
822 if (isPrewarmed == WebProcessProxy::IsPrewarmed::Yes) {
823 ASSERT(!m_prewarmedProcess);
824 m_prewarmedProcess = makeWeakPtr(process);
825 }
826
827#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY) && !PLATFORM(MACCATALYST)
828 process.send(Messages::WebProcess::BacklightLevelDidChange(displayBrightness()), 0);
829#endif
830
831#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
832 process.sendAudioComponentRegistrations();
833#endif
834
835#if PLATFORM(MAC)
836 registerDisplayConfigurationCallback();
837#endif
838
839 registerHighDynamicRangeChangeCallback();
840}

847 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(PerformanceLogging, "prewarmProcess: Prewarming a WebProcess for performance");
848 createNewWebProcess(nullptr, WebProcessProxy::IsPrewarmed::Yes);

851void WebProcessPool::enableProcessTermination()
852{
853 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(Process, "enableProcessTermination:");
854 m_processTerminationEnabled = true;
855 Vector<Ref<WebProcessProxy>> processes = m_processes;
856 for (auto& process : processes) {
857 if (shouldTerminate(process))
858 process->terminate();
859 }
860}

862void WebProcessPool::disableProcessTermination()
863{
864 if (!m_processTerminationEnabled)
865 return;
866
867 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(Process, "disableProcessTermination:");
868 m_processTerminationEnabled = false;
869}
870
871bool WebProcessPool::shouldTerminate(WebProcessProxy& process)
872{
873 ASSERT(m_processes.contains(process));
874
875 if (!m_processTerminationEnabled || m_configuration->alwaysKeepAndReuseSwappedProcesses())
876 return false;
877
878 return true;
879}
880
881void WebProcessPool::processDidFinishLaunching(WebProcessProxy& process)
882{
883 ASSERT(m_processes.contains(process));
884
885 if (!m_visitedLinksPopulated) {
886 populateVisitedLinks();
887 m_visitedLinksPopulated = true;
888 }
889
890 // Sometimes the memorySampler gets initialized after process initialization has happened but before the process has finished launching
891 // so check if it needs to be started here
892 if (m_memorySamplerEnabled) {
893 SandboxExtension::Handle sampleLogSandboxHandle;
894 WallTime now = WallTime::now();
895 auto sampleLogFilePath = makeString("WebProcess", static_cast<unsigned long long>(now.secondsSinceEpoch().seconds()), "pid", process.processIdentifier());
896 sampleLogFilePath = SandboxExtension::createHandleForTemporaryFile(sampleLogFilePath, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, sampleLogSandboxHandle);
897
898 process.send(Messages::WebProcess::StartMemorySampler(sampleLogSandboxHandle, sampleLogFilePath, m_memorySamplerInterval), 0);
899 }
900
901 if (m_configuration->fullySynchronousModeIsAllowedForTesting())
902 process.connection()->allowFullySynchronousModeForTesting();
903
904 if (m_configuration->ignoreSynchronousMessagingTimeoutsForTesting())
905 process.connection()->ignoreTimeoutsForTesting();
906
907 m_connectionClient.didCreateConnection(this, process.webConnection());
908}
909
910void WebProcessPool::disconnectProcess(WebProcessProxy& process)
911{
912 ASSERT(m_processes.contains(process));
913
914 if (m_prewarmedProcess == &process) {
915 ASSERT(m_prewarmedProcess->isPrewarmed());
916 m_prewarmedProcess = nullptr;
917 } else if (process.isDummyProcessProxy()) {
918 auto removedProcess = m_dummyProcessProxies.take(process.sessionID());
919 ASSERT_UNUSED(removedProcess, removedProcess == &process);
920 }
921
922 // FIXME (Multi-WebProcess): <rdar://problem/12239765> Some of the invalidation calls of the other supplements are still necessary in multi-process mode, but they should only affect data structures pertaining to the process being disconnected.
923 // Clearing everything causes assertion failures, so it's less trouble to skip that for now.
924 Ref<WebProcessProxy> protectedProcess(process);
925
926 m_backForwardCache->removeEntriesForProcess(process);
927
928#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
929 if (process.isRunningServiceWorkers())
930 removeFromServiceWorkerProcesses(process);
931#endif
932
933 static_cast<WebContextSupplement*>(supplement<WebGeolocationManagerProxy>())->processDidClose(&process);
934
935 m_processes.removeFirst(process);
936
937#if ENABLE(GAMEPAD)
938 if (m_processesUsingGamepads.contains(process))
939 processStoppedUsingGamepads(process);
940#endif
941
942 removeProcessFromOriginCacheSet(process);
943}

945Ref<WebProcessProxy> WebProcessPool::processForRegistrableDomain(WebsiteDataStore& websiteDataStore, WebPageProxy* page, const RegistrableDomain& registrableDomain)
946{
947 if (!registrableDomain.isEmpty()) {
948 if (auto process = webProcessCache().takeProcess(registrableDomain, websiteDataStore)) {
949 ASSERT(m_processes.contains(*process));
950 return process.releaseNonNull();
951 }
952
953 // Check if we have a suspended page for the given registrable domain and use its process if we do, for performance reasons.
954 if (auto process = SuspendedPageProxy::findReusableSuspendedPageProcess(*this, registrableDomain, websiteDataStore)) {
955 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSwapping, "processForRegistrableDomain: Using WebProcess from a SuspendedPage (process=%p, PID=%i)", process.get(), process->processIdentifier());
956 ASSERT(m_processes.contains(*process));
957 return process.releaseNonNull();
958 }
959 }
960
961 if (auto process = tryTakePrewarmedProcess(websiteDataStore)) {
962 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSwapping, "processForRegistrableDomain: Using prewarmed process (process=%p, PID=%i)", process.get(), process->processIdentifier());
963 if (!registrableDomain.isEmpty())
964 tryPrewarmWithDomainInformation(*process, registrableDomain);
965 ASSERT(m_processes.contains(*process));
966 return process.releaseNonNull();
967 }
968
969 if (usesSingleWebProcess()) {
970#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
971 bool mustMatchDataStore = WebKit::WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStoreExists() && &websiteDataStore != WebKit::WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStore().ptr();
972#else
973 bool mustMatchDataStore = false;
974#endif
975
976 for (auto& process : m_processes) {
977 if (process.ptr() == m_prewarmedProcess.get() || process->isDummyProcessProxy())
978 continue;
979#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
980 if (process->isRunningServiceWorkers())
981 continue;
982#endif
983 if (mustMatchDataStore && &process->websiteDataStore() != &websiteDataStore)
984 continue;
985 return process;
986 }
987 }
988 return createNewWebProcess(&websiteDataStore);
989}

991#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
992UserContentControllerIdentifier WebProcessPool::userContentControllerIdentifierForServiceWorkers()
993{
994 if (!m_userContentControllerForServiceWorker)
995 m_userContentControllerForServiceWorker = WebUserContentControllerProxy::create();
996
997 return m_userContentControllerForServiceWorker->identifier();
998}

1001Ref<WebPageProxy> WebProcessPool::createWebPage(PageClient& pageClient, Ref<API::PageConfiguration>&& pageConfiguration)
1002{
1003 if (!pageConfiguration->pageGroup())
1004 pageConfiguration->setPageGroup(m_defaultPageGroup.ptr());
1005 if (!pageConfiguration->preferences())
1006 pageConfiguration->setPreferences(&pageConfiguration->pageGroup()->preferences());
1007 if (!pageConfiguration->userContentController())
1008 pageConfiguration->setUserContentController(&pageConfiguration->pageGroup()->userContentController());
1009 if (!pageConfiguration->visitedLinkStore())
1010 pageConfiguration->setVisitedLinkStore(m_visitedLinkStore.ptr());
1011
1012 if (!pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore()) {
1013 // We try to avoid creating the default data store as long as possible.
1014 // But if there is an attempt to create a web page without any specified data store, then we have to create it.
1015 pageConfiguration->setWebsiteDataStore(WebKit::WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStore().ptr());
1016 }
1017
1018 RefPtr<WebProcessProxy> process;
1019 auto* relatedPage = pageConfiguration->relatedPage();
1020 if (relatedPage && !relatedPage->isClosed()) {
1021 // Sharing processes, e.g. when creating the page via window.open().
1022 process = &pageConfiguration->relatedPage()->ensureRunningProcess();
1023 // We do not support several WebsiteDataStores sharing a single process.
1024 ASSERT(process->isDummyProcessProxy() || pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore() == &process->websiteDataStore());
1025 ASSERT(&pageConfiguration->relatedPage()->websiteDataStore() == pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore());
1026 } else if (!m_isDelayedWebProcessLaunchDisabled) {
1027 // In the common case, we delay process launch until something is actually loaded in the page.
1028 process = dummyProcessProxy(pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore()->sessionID());
1029 if (!process) {
1030 process = WebProcessProxy::create(*this, pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore(), WebProcessProxy::IsPrewarmed::No, WebProcessProxy::ShouldLaunchProcess::No);
1031 m_dummyProcessProxies.add(pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore()->sessionID(), makeWeakPtr(*process));
1032 m_processes.append(*process);
1033 }
1034 } else
1035 process = processForRegistrableDomain(*pageConfiguration->websiteDataStore(), nullptr, { });
1036
1037 RefPtr<WebUserContentControllerProxy> userContentController = pageConfiguration->userContentController();
1038
1039 ASSERT(process);
1040
1041 auto page = process->createWebPage(pageClient, WTFMove(pageConfiguration));
1042
1043#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
1044 if (!m_serviceWorkerPreferences) {
1045 m_serviceWorkerPreferences = page->preferencesStore();
1046 for (auto& serviceWorkerProcess : serviceWorkerProcesses())
1047 serviceWorkerProcess.updateServiceWorkerPreferencesStore(*m_serviceWorkerPreferences);
1048 }
1049 if (userContentController)
1050 m_userContentControllerForServiceWorker = userContentController;
1051#endif
1052
1053 bool enableProcessSwapOnCrossSiteNavigation = page->preferences().processSwapOnCrossSiteNavigationEnabled();
1054#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1055 if (WebCore::IOSApplication::isFirefox() && !linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstWithProcessSwapOnCrossSiteNavigation))
1056 enableProcessSwapOnCrossSiteNavigation = false;
1057#endif
1058
1059 bool wasProcessSwappingOnNavigationEnabled = m_configuration->processSwapsOnNavigation();
1060 m_configuration->setProcessSwapsOnNavigationFromExperimentalFeatures(enableProcessSwapOnCrossSiteNavigation);
1061 if (wasProcessSwappingOnNavigationEnabled != m_configuration->processSwapsOnNavigation())
1062 m_webProcessCache->updateCapacity(*this);
1063
1064#if ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
1065 if (auto* gpuProcess = GPUProcessProxy::singletonIfCreated())
1066 gpuProcess->updatePreferences();
1067#endif
1068
1069 return page;
1070}

1075 if (m_serviceWorkerUserAgent == userAgent)

1083void WebProcessPool::pageBeginUsingWebsiteDataStore(WebPageProxyIdentifier pageID, WebsiteDataStore& dataStore)
1084{
1085 RELEASE_ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1086 RELEASE_ASSERT(m_sessionToPageIDsMap.isValidKey(dataStore.sessionID()));
1087 auto result = m_sessionToPageIDsMap.add(dataStore.sessionID(), HashSet<WebPageProxyIdentifier>()).iterator->value.add(pageID);
1088 ASSERT_UNUSED(result, result.isNewEntry);
1089}
1090
1091void WebProcessPool::pageEndUsingWebsiteDataStore(WebPageProxyIdentifier pageID, WebsiteDataStore& dataStore)
1092{
1093 RELEASE_ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1094 auto sessionID = dataStore.sessionID();
1095 RELEASE_ASSERT(m_sessionToPageIDsMap.isValidKey(dataStore.sessionID()));
1096 auto iterator = m_sessionToPageIDsMap.find(sessionID);
1097 RELEASE_ASSERT(iterator != m_sessionToPageIDsMap.end());
1098
1099 auto takenPageID = iterator->value.take(pageID);
1100 ASSERT_UNUSED(takenPageID, takenPageID == pageID);
1101
1102 if (iterator->value.isEmpty()) {
1103 m_sessionToPageIDsMap.remove(iterator);
1104
1105 if (sessionID.isEphemeral())
1106 m_webProcessCache->clearAllProcessesForSession(sessionID);
1107 }
1108}

1113 RELEASE_ASSERT(m_sessionToPageIDsMap.isValidKey(dataStore.sessionID()));
1114 return m_sessionToPageIDsMap.contains(dataStore.sessionID());
1115}

1117DownloadProxy& WebProcessPool::download(WebsiteDataStore& dataStore, WebPageProxy* initiatingPage, const ResourceRequest& request, const String& suggestedFilename)
1118{
1119 auto& downloadProxy = createDownloadProxy(dataStore, request, initiatingPage, { });
1120
1121 std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isAppBound = NavigatingToAppBoundDomain::No;
1122 if (initiatingPage) {
1123 initiatingPage->handleDownloadRequest(downloadProxy);
1124#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
1125 isAppBound = initiatingPage->isTopFrameNavigatingToAppBoundDomain();
1126#endif
1127 }
1128
1129 ResourceRequest updatedRequest(request);
1130 // Request's firstPartyForCookies will be used as Original URL of the download request.
1131 // We set the value to top level document's URL.
1132 if (initiatingPage) {
1133 URL initiatingPageURL = URL { URL { }, initiatingPage->pageLoadState().url() };
1134 updatedRequest.setFirstPartyForCookies(initiatingPageURL);
1135 updatedRequest.setIsSameSite(areRegistrableDomainsEqual(initiatingPageURL, request.url()));
1136 if (!updatedRequest.hasHTTPHeaderField(HTTPHeaderName::UserAgent))
1137 updatedRequest.setHTTPUserAgent(initiatingPage->userAgentForURL(request.url()));
1138 } else {
1139 updatedRequest.setFirstPartyForCookies(URL());
1140 updatedRequest.setIsSameSite(false);
1141 if (!updatedRequest.hasHTTPHeaderField(HTTPHeaderName::UserAgent))
1142 updatedRequest.setHTTPUserAgent(WebPageProxy::standardUserAgent());
1143 }
1144 updatedRequest.setIsTopSite(false);
1145 dataStore.networkProcess().send(Messages::NetworkProcess::DownloadRequest(dataStore.sessionID(), downloadProxy.downloadID(), updatedRequest, isAppBound, suggestedFilename), 0);
1146
1147 return downloadProxy;
1148}
1149
1150DownloadProxy& WebProcessPool::resumeDownload(WebsiteDataStore& dataStore, WebPageProxy* initiatingPage, const API::Data& resumeData, const String& path, CallDownloadDidStart callDownloadDidStart)
1151{
1152 auto& downloadProxy = createDownloadProxy(dataStore, ResourceRequest(), initiatingPage, { });
1153
1154 SandboxExtension::Handle sandboxExtensionHandle;
1155 if (!path.isEmpty())
1156 SandboxExtension::createHandle(path, SandboxExtension::Type::ReadWrite, sandboxExtensionHandle);
1157
1158 dataStore.networkProcess().send(Messages::NetworkProcess::ResumeDownload(dataStore.sessionID(), downloadProxy.downloadID(), resumeData.dataReference(), path, sandboxExtensionHandle, callDownloadDidStart), 0);
1159 return downloadProxy;
1160}

1170void WebProcessPool::didReachGoodTimeToPrewarm()
1171{
1172 if (!configuration().isAutomaticProcessWarmingEnabled() || !configuration().processSwapsOnNavigation() || usesSingleWebProcess())
1173 return;
1174
1175 if (MemoryPressureHandler::singleton().isUnderMemoryPressure()) {
1176 if (!m_prewarmedProcess)
1177 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(PerformanceLogging, "didReachGoodTimeToPrewarm: Not automatically prewarming a WebProcess due to memory pressure");
1178 return;
1179 }
1180
1181 prewarmProcess();
1182}

1196void WebProcessPool::handleMemoryPressureWarning(Critical)
1197{
1198 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(PerformanceLogging, "handleMemoryPressureWarning:");
1199
1200 // Clear back/forward cache first as processes removed from the back/forward cache will likely
1201 // be added to the WebProcess cache.
1202 m_backForwardCache->clear();
1203 m_webProcessCache->clear();
1204
1205 if (m_prewarmedProcess)
1206 m_prewarmedProcess->shutDown();
1207 ASSERT(!m_prewarmedProcess);
1208}

1520static WebProcessProxy* webProcessProxyFromConnection(IPC::Connection& connection, const Vector<Ref<WebProcessProxy>>& processes)
1521{
1522 for (auto& process : processes) {
1523 if (process->hasConnection(connection))
1524 return process.ptr();
1525 }
1526
1527 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1528 return nullptr;
1529}

1531void WebProcessPool::handleMessage(IPC::Connection& connection, const String& messageName, const WebKit::UserData& messageBody)
1532{
1533 auto* webProcessProxy = webProcessProxyFromConnection(connection, m_processes);
1534 if (!webProcessProxy)
1535 return;
1536 m_injectedBundleClient->didReceiveMessageFromInjectedBundle(*this, messageName, webProcessProxy->transformHandlesToObjects(messageBody.object()).get());
1537}
1538
1539void WebProcessPool::handleSynchronousMessage(IPC::Connection& connection, const String& messageName, const UserData& messageBody, CompletionHandler<void(UserData&&)>&& completionHandler)
1540{
1541 auto* webProcessProxy = webProcessProxyFromConnection(connection, m_processes);
1542 if (!webProcessProxy)
1543 return completionHandler({ });
1544
1545 m_injectedBundleClient->didReceiveSynchronousMessageFromInjectedBundle(*this, messageName, webProcessProxy->transformHandlesToObjects(messageBody.object()).get(), [webProcessProxy = makeRef(*webProcessProxy), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (RefPtr<API::Object>&& returnData) mutable {
1546 completionHandler(UserData(webProcessProxy->transformObjectsToHandles(returnData.get())));
1547 });
1548}

1552void WebProcessPool::startedUsingGamepads(IPC::Connection& connection)
1553{
1554 auto* proxy = webProcessProxyFromConnection(connection, m_processes);
1555 if (!proxy)
1556 return;
1557

1559
1560 ASSERT(!m_processesUsingGamepads.contains(*proxy));
1561 m_processesUsingGamepads.add(proxy);
1562
1563 if (!wereAnyProcessesUsingGamepads)
1564 UIGamepadProvider::singleton().processPoolStartedUsingGamepads(*this);

1572 if (!proxy)
1573 return;
1574
1575 ASSERT(m_processesUsingGamepads.contains(*proxy));
1576 processStoppedUsingGamepads(*proxy);
1577}
1578
1579void WebProcessPool::processStoppedUsingGamepads(WebProcessProxy& process)
1580{
1581 bool wereAnyProcessesUsingGamepads = !m_processesUsingGamepads.computesEmpty();
1582
1583 ASSERT(m_processesUsingGamepads.contains(process));
1584 m_processesUsingGamepads.remove(process);
1585
1586 if (wereAnyProcessesUsingGamepads && m_processesUsingGamepads.computesEmpty())
1587 UIGamepadProvider::singleton().processPoolStoppedUsingGamepads(*this);
1588}

1686void WebProcessPool::updateHiddenPageThrottlingAutoIncreaseLimit()
1687{
1688 // We're estimating an upper bound for a set of background timer fires for a page to be 200ms
1689 // (including all timer fires, all paging-in, and any resulting GC). To ensure this does not
1690 // result in more than 1% CPU load allow for one timer fire per 100x this duration.
1691 static int maximumTimerThrottlePerPageInMS = 200 * 100;
1692
1693 int limitInMilliseconds = maximumTimerThrottlePerPageInMS * m_hiddenPageThrottlingAutoIncreasesCounter.value();
1694 sendToAllProcesses(Messages::WebProcess::SetHiddenPageDOMTimerThrottlingIncreaseLimit(limitInMilliseconds));
1695}

1746void WebProcessPool::addProcessToOriginCacheSet(WebProcessProxy& process, const URL& url)
1747{
1748 auto registrableDomain = WebCore::RegistrableDomain { url };
1749 auto result = m_swappedProcessesPerRegistrableDomain.add(registrableDomain, &process);
1750 if (!result.isNewEntry)
1751 result.iterator->value = &process;
1752
1753 LOG(ProcessSwapping, "(ProcessSwapping) Registrable domain %s just saved a cached process with pid %i", registrableDomain.string().utf8().data(), process.processIdentifier());
1754 if (!result.isNewEntry)
1755 LOG(ProcessSwapping, "(ProcessSwapping) Note: It already had one saved");
1756}
1757
1758void WebProcessPool::removeProcessFromOriginCacheSet(WebProcessProxy& process)
1759{
1760 LOG(ProcessSwapping, "(ProcessSwapping) Removing process with pid %i from the origin cache set", process.processIdentifier());
1761
1762 // FIXME: This can be very inefficient as the number of remembered origins and processes grows
1763 Vector<WebCore::RegistrableDomain> registrableDomainsToRemove;
1764 for (auto entry : m_swappedProcessesPerRegistrableDomain) {
1765 if (entry.value == &process)
1766 registrableDomainsToRemove.append(entry.key);
1767 }
1768
1769 for (auto& registrableDomain : registrableDomainsToRemove)
1770 m_swappedProcessesPerRegistrableDomain.remove(registrableDomain);
1771}
1772
1773void WebProcessPool::processForNavigation(WebPageProxy& page, const API::Navigation& navigation, Ref<WebProcessProxy>&& sourceProcess, const URL& sourceURL, ProcessSwapRequestedByClient processSwapRequestedByClient, Ref<WebsiteDataStore>&& dataStore, CompletionHandler<void(Ref<WebProcessProxy>&&, SuspendedPageProxy*, const String&)>&& completionHandler)
1774{
1775 processForNavigationInternal(page, navigation, sourceProcess.copyRef(), sourceURL, processSwapRequestedByClient, WTFMove(dataStore), [this, page = makeRefPtr(page), navigation = makeRef(navigation), sourceProcess = sourceProcess.copyRef(), sourceURL, processSwapRequestedByClient, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](Ref<WebProcessProxy>&& process, SuspendedPageProxy* suspendedPage, const String& reason) mutable {
1776 // We are process-swapping so automatic process prewarming would be beneficial if the client has not explicitly enabled / disabled it.
1777 bool doingAnAutomaticProcessSwap = processSwapRequestedByClient == ProcessSwapRequestedByClient::No && process.ptr() != sourceProcess.ptr();
1778 if (doingAnAutomaticProcessSwap && !configuration().wasAutomaticProcessWarmingSetByClient() && !configuration().clientWouldBenefitFromAutomaticProcessPrewarming()) {
1779 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(PerformanceLogging, "processForNavigation: Automatically turning on process prewarming because the client would benefit from it");
1780 configuration().setClientWouldBenefitFromAutomaticProcessPrewarming(true);
1781 }
1782
1783 if (m_configuration->alwaysKeepAndReuseSwappedProcesses() && process.ptr() != sourceProcess.ptr()) {
1784 static std::once_flag onceFlag;
1785 std::call_once(onceFlag, [] {
1786 WTFLogAlways("WARNING: The option to always keep swapped web processes alive is active. This is meant for debugging and testing only.");
1787 });
1788
1789 addProcessToOriginCacheSet(sourceProcess, sourceURL);
1790
1791 LOG(ProcessSwapping, "(ProcessSwapping) Navigating from %s to %s, keeping around old process. Now holding on to old processes for %u origins.", sourceURL.string().utf8().data(), navigation->currentRequest().url().string().utf8().data(), m_swappedProcessesPerRegistrableDomain.size());
1792 }
1793
1794 completionHandler(WTFMove(process), suspendedPage, reason);
1795 });
1796}
1797
1798void WebProcessPool::processForNavigationInternal(WebPageProxy& page, const API::Navigation& navigation, Ref<WebProcessProxy>&& sourceProcess, const URL& pageSourceURL, ProcessSwapRequestedByClient processSwapRequestedByClient, Ref<WebsiteDataStore>&& dataStore, CompletionHandler<void(Ref<WebProcessProxy>&&, SuspendedPageProxy*, const String&)>&& completionHandler)
1799{
1800 auto& targetURL = navigation.currentRequest().url();
1801 auto targetRegistrableDomain = WebCore::RegistrableDomain { targetURL };
1802
1803 auto createNewProcess = [this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), page = makeRef(page), targetRegistrableDomain, dataStore] () -> Ref<WebProcessProxy> {
1804 return processForRegistrableDomain(dataStore, page.ptr(), targetRegistrableDomain);
1805 };
1806
1807 if (usesSingleWebProcess())
1808 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Single WebProcess mode is enabled"_s);
1809
1810 if (processSwapRequestedByClient == ProcessSwapRequestedByClient::Yes)
1811 return completionHandler(createNewProcess(), nullptr, "Process swap was requested by the client"_s);
1812
1813 if (!m_configuration->processSwapsOnNavigation())
1814 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Feature is disabled"_s);
1815
1816 if (m_automationSession)
1817 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "An automation session is active"_s);
1818
1819 if (!sourceProcess->hasCommittedAnyProvisionalLoads()) {
1820 tryPrewarmWithDomainInformation(sourceProcess, targetRegistrableDomain);
1821 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Process has not yet committed any provisional loads"_s);
1822 }
1823
1824 // FIXME: We should support process swap when a window has been opened via window.open() without 'noopener'.
1825 // The issue is that the opener has a handle to the WindowProxy.
1826 if (navigation.openedByDOMWithOpener() && !m_configuration->processSwapsOnWindowOpenWithOpener())
1827 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Browsing context been opened by DOM without 'noopener'"_s);
1828
1829 // FIXME: We should support process swap when a window has opened other windows via window.open.
1830 if (navigation.hasOpenedFrames())
1831 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Browsing context has opened other windows"_s);
1832
1833 if (auto* targetItem = navigation.targetItem()) {
1834 if (auto* suspendedPage = targetItem->suspendedPage()) {
1835 return suspendedPage->waitUntilReadyToUnsuspend([createNewProcess = WTFMove(createNewProcess), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](SuspendedPageProxy* suspendedPage) mutable {
1836 if (!suspendedPage)
1837 return completionHandler(createNewProcess(), nullptr, "Using new process because target back/forward item's suspended page is not reusable"_s);
1838 Ref<WebProcessProxy> process = suspendedPage->process();
1839 completionHandler(WTFMove(process), suspendedPage, "Using target back/forward item's process and suspended page"_s);
1840 });
1841 }
1842
1843 if (RefPtr<WebProcessProxy> process = WebProcessProxy::processForIdentifier(targetItem->lastProcessIdentifier())) {
1844 if (process->state() != WebProcessProxy::State::Terminated) {
1845 // Make sure we remove the process from the cache if it is in there since we're about to use it.
1846 if (process->isInProcessCache()) {
1847 webProcessCache().removeProcess(*process, WebProcessCache::ShouldShutDownProcess::No);
1848 ASSERT(!process->isInProcessCache());
1849 }
1850
1851 return completionHandler(process.releaseNonNull(), nullptr, "Using target back/forward item's process"_s);
1852 }
1853 }
1854 }
1855
1856 if (navigation.treatAsSameOriginNavigation())
1857 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "The treatAsSameOriginNavigation flag is set"_s);
1858
1859 URL sourceURL;
1860 if (page.isPageOpenedByDOMShowingInitialEmptyDocument() && !navigation.requesterOrigin().isEmpty())
1861 sourceURL = URL { URL(), navigation.requesterOrigin().toString() };
1862 else
1863 sourceURL = pageSourceURL;
1864
1865 if (sourceURL.isEmpty() && page.configuration().relatedPage()) {
1866 sourceURL = URL { { }, page.configuration().relatedPage()->pageLoadState().url() };
1867 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSwapping, "processForNavigationInternal: Using related page's URL as source URL for process swap decision (page=%p)", page.configuration().relatedPage());
1868 }
1869
1870 // For non-HTTP(s) URLs, we only swap when navigating to a new scheme, unless processSwapsOnNavigationWithinSameNonHTTPFamilyProtocol is set.
1871 if (!m_configuration->processSwapsOnNavigationWithinSameNonHTTPFamilyProtocol() && !sourceURL.protocolIsInHTTPFamily() && sourceURL.protocol() == targetURL.protocol())
1872 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Navigation within the same non-HTTP(s) protocol"_s);
1873
1874 if (!sourceURL.isValid() || !targetURL.isValid() || sourceURL.isEmpty() || sourceURL.protocolIsAbout() || targetRegistrableDomain.matches(sourceURL))
1875 return completionHandler(WTFMove(sourceProcess), nullptr, "Navigation is same-site"_s);
1876
1877 String reason = "Navigation is cross-site"_s;
1878
1879 if (m_configuration->alwaysKeepAndReuseSwappedProcesses()) {
1880 LOG(ProcessSwapping, "(ProcessSwapping) Considering re-use of a previously cached process for domain %s", targetRegistrableDomain.string().utf8().data());
1881
1882 if (auto* process = m_swappedProcessesPerRegistrableDomain.get(targetRegistrableDomain)) {
1883 if (&process->websiteDataStore() == dataStore.ptr()) {
1884 LOG(ProcessSwapping, "(ProcessSwapping) Reusing a previously cached process with pid %i to continue navigation to URL %s", process->processIdentifier(), targetURL.string().utf8().data());
1885
1886 return completionHandler(makeRef(*process), nullptr, reason);
1887 }
1888 }
1889 }
1890
1891 return completionHandler(createNewProcess(), nullptr, reason);
1892}

1952void WebProcessPool::didCollectPrewarmInformation(const WebCore::RegistrableDomain& registrableDomain, const WebCore::PrewarmInformation& prewarmInformation)
1953{
1954 static const size_t maximumSizeToPreventUnlimitedGrowth = 100;
1955 if (m_prewarmInformationPerRegistrableDomain.size() == maximumSizeToPreventUnlimitedGrowth)
1956 m_prewarmInformationPerRegistrableDomain.remove(m_prewarmInformationPerRegistrableDomain.random());
1957
1958 auto& value = m_prewarmInformationPerRegistrableDomain.ensure(registrableDomain, [] {
1959 return makeUnique<WebCore::PrewarmInformation>();
1960 }).iterator->value;
1961
1962 *value = prewarmInformation;
1963}

1965void WebProcessPool::tryPrewarmWithDomainInformation(WebProcessProxy& process, const RegistrableDomain& registrableDomain)
1966{
1967 auto* prewarmInformation = m_prewarmInformationPerRegistrableDomain.get(registrableDomain);
1968 if (!prewarmInformation)
1969 return;
1970 process.send(Messages::WebProcess::PrewarmWithDomainInformation(*prewarmInformation), 0);
1971}

2018void WebProcessPool::updateAudibleMediaAssertions()
2019{
2020 if (!m_webProcessWithAudibleMediaCounter.value()) {
2021 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSuspension, "updateAudibleMediaAssertions: The number of processes playing audible media now zero. Releasing UI process assertion.");
2022 m_audibleMediaActivity = std::nullopt;
2023 return;
2024 }
2025
2026 if (m_audibleMediaActivity)
2027 return;
2028
2029 WEBPROCESSPOOL_RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSuspension, "updateAudibleMediaAssertions: The number of processes playing audible media is now greater than zero. Taking UI process assertion.");
2030 m_audibleMediaActivity = AudibleMediaActivity {
2031 makeUniqueRef<ProcessAssertion>(getCurrentProcessID(), "WebKit Media Playback"_s, ProcessAssertionType::MediaPlayback)
2032#if ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
2033 , gpuProcess() ? makeUnique<ProcessAssertion>(gpuProcess()->processIdentifier(), "WebKit Media Playback"_s, ProcessAssertionType::MediaPlayback) : nullptr
2034#endif
2035 };
2036}
